name: Wookiee Strangle (V)
Lore: 'Wookiees have been known to dislocate more than just arms.',
Text: 'Once per game, during your move phase, target opponent''s character present with your Wookiee. Both players draw destiny. Add Wookiee''s power; opponent adds target''s defense value. Target lost if your total destiny +2 > opponent''s total destiny.',
